<div class="row">
  <div class="col col-md-8 col-sm-12 main">
<h1>Rate the candidates</h1>
<h5>Start with the Ministry Portfolios in your hand. Select one, then click on that person's name.<br>
  Please don't skip anyone. If you've decided a certain candidate is not good for St. Paul's, click his or 
  her name and go to the last line of the survey questions and make a statement to that effect. 
  This way we will know no one was overlooked.
  </h5>
  <p><strong>Problems? Call Tom, 285-9224</strong></p>
  <% @candidates.each do |can| %>
    <h2>The Rev. <%=link_to can.full_name, can.url %></h2>
    <hr>
  <% end %>  
<div class="mt100"></div>
