  <h2>Leadership Qualities</h2>
    <p> Keywords: <i> Compassionate, Accessible, Outreacher,  Stewardship 
    promotor, Formation facilitator, Possessor of sense of humor, motivator,
    financial experience and interest, self-starter, delegator, grower, 
    energetic and resillient, pastoral </i></p>
     <p> <%= link_to "Add your question for this category", 
        edit_characteristic_path(leader) %></p>
  <% end %>

  <div class="mt50"></div>
  <% @characteristics.where(kind: "communications").take(1).each do|com| %>  
    <h2>Communications style</h2>
    <p>Keywords: <i> worship and music style, preaching style, liturgical style, 
    formation style</i><p>
